From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mykola Lysenko <mykolal@meta.com>
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2026 11:25:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] selftests/bpf: include btf_ptr.h in bpf_iter_task_btf

bpf_iter_task_btf.c declares a local struct btf_ptr variable. Some
generated vmlinux.h variants only forward-declare struct btf_ptr, which
leaves the selftest with an incomplete type at compile time.

Other BPF selftests that use struct btf_ptr include btf_ptr.h directly.
Do the same here so the program does not depend on vmlinux.h carrying the
full helper type definition.

Signed-off-by: Mykola Lysenko <mykolal@meta.com>
---
 tools/testing/selftests/bpf/progs/bpf_iter_task_btf.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/tools/testing/selftests/bpf/progs/bpf_iter_task_btf.c b/tools/testing/selftests/bpf/progs/bpf_iter_task_btf.c
index ef2f7c8d9373..b1517a0d6a3e 100644
--- a/tools/testing/selftests/bpf/progs/bpf_iter_task_btf.c
+++ b/tools/testing/selftests/bpf/progs/bpf_iter_task_btf.c
@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@
 // SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
 /* Copyright (c) 2020, Oracle and/or its affiliates. */
-#include <vmlinux.h>
+#include "btf_ptr.h"
 #include <bpf/bpf_helpers.h>
 #include <bpf/bpf_core_read.h>
 
-- 
2.53.0
